data.judul: How to Get YouTube API Key
data.deskripsi:
Easy Way to Create YouTube API Key or YouTube Data API v3 in 2023 Thank You so Much for Watching, If This Videos Helpful Then Please Like & Comment https://youtu.be/N18czV5tj5o
✪ Post Here: https://bit.ly/2O0PZFM

✪ Steps to Get YouTube API Key ( YouTube Data API v3 )

- Sign in to Google Console Cloud
https://console.cloud.google.com
- Create project or Select Project for API Key
- Click on Navigation Menu ( top left corner )
- Go To API'S and Services
https://console.cloud.google.com/apis
- Select Your  project and Go to Library
https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library
- Scroll down & then Click on YouTube Data API V3 https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/youtube.googleapis.com
- Click on Enable  YouTube Data API V3
- Now We Need to Create Credentials for our YouTube API Key
- Click on Credentials
- Click on Create Credentials
- Click on API Key
- now You will get Your YouTube API key, simply copy it & use wherever you want.
- Done
